## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="35bff-102">使用<xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.StopStoryboard>操作并提供<xref:System.Windows.EventTrigger>或<xref:System.Windows.Trigger>若要以交互方式停止<xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="35bff-102">Use a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.StopStoryboard> action with an <xref:System.Windows.EventTrigger> or <xref:System.Windows.Trigger> to interactively stop a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="35bff-103"><xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.StopStoryboard> 只会影响<xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard>处于活动状态 (后<xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard>启动)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="35bff-103"><xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.StopStoryboard> only affects a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard> when it is active (after the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard> starts).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="35bff-104">正在停止情节提要触发器<xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline.CurrentGlobalSpeedInvalidated>并<xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline.CurrentStateInvalidated>事件，但不是<xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline.Completed>事件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="35bff-104">Stopping a storyboard triggers the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline.CurrentGlobalSpeedInvalidated> and <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline.CurrentStateInvalidated> events, but not the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline.Completed> event.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="35bff-105"><xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.PauseStoryboard> 不引用<xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard>直接。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="35bff-105"><xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.PauseStoryboard> does not reference a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard> directly.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="35bff-106">而是<xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.PauseStoryboard>必须引用<xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Name%2A>的<xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard>控制<xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="35bff-106">Rather, <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.PauseStoryboard> must reference the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Name%2A> of the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard> that controls the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="35bff-107">请参阅[如何： 使用事件触发器来控制情节提要启动之后](~/docs/framework/wpf/graphics-multimedia/how-to-use-event-triggers-to-control-a-storyboard-after-it-starts.md)有关的示例。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="35bff-107">See [How to: Use Event Triggers to Control a Storyboard After It Starts](~/docs/framework/wpf/graphics-multimedia/how-to-use-event-triggers-to-control-a-storyboard-after-it-starts.md) for an example.</span></span>  
  
## <a name="pause-resume-stop-or-otherwise-control-a-storyboard-interactively"></a><span data-ttu-id="35bff-108">暂停、 恢复、 停止或以其他方式以交互方式控制情节提要</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="35bff-108">Pause, Resume, Stop, or Otherwise Control a Storyboard Interactively</span></span>  
 <span data-ttu-id="35bff-109">可以暂停、 恢复或以其他方式控制<xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Storyboard%2A>以交互方式，设置<xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Name%2A>的属性及其<xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard>，并使用<xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ControllableStoryboardAction>对象 (如<xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.PauseStoryboard>， <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ResumeStoryboard>，或<xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.StopStoryboard>) 通过其进行控制引用其<xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Name%2A>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="35bff-109">To be able to pause, resume, or otherwise control a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Storyboard%2A> interactively, set the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Name%2A> property of its <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard> and use a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ControllableStoryboardAction> object (such as <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.PauseStoryboard>, <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ResumeStoryboard>, or <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.StopStoryboard>) to control it by referencing its <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Name%2A>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="35bff-110">如果<xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Name%2A>的<xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard>未指定，<xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Storyboard%2A>开始后不能以交互方式控制。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="35bff-110">If the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Name%2A> of <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard> is unspecified, the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Storyboard%2A> cannot be interactively controlled after it is begun.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="35bff-111">请参阅[如何： 使用事件触发器来控制情节提要启动之后](~/docs/framework/wpf/graphics-multimedia/how-to-use-event-triggers-to-control-a-storyboard-after-it-starts